  <h1 class="gd-h1">How to Ski Powder</h1>
  <p class="gd-lede">Skiing powder is one of the great joys on snow, and it is a skill you can genuinely learn. This practical guide walks through the technique, the mindset and the drills that turn deep snow from intimidating to effortless, so you arrive ready for our <a href="/packages">packages</a> and the endless open faces of <a href="/iceland">Iceland</a>.</p>
